metadata.name: Take a chance, let me show you the world
metadata.description:
In life, we are always afraid to venture beyond our comfort bubble.
We never know how life pans out, things happen and people happen for a reason.
Live with no regrets - Be willing to try, to venture, to see, to feel, and don't be afraid of letting others into your life. 
The world is bigger than both you and me, take a chance, go see what you're missing out on.
